post.content:
Hello Band Families!

For those that have not picked up their Band Picture Buttons, I will be in the cafeteria (by the band room) to hand out buttons THIS Wednesday night (9/7) AFTER the 6-9 practice. Since this weekend is an away game, if you don’t pick them up on Wednesday night, you will have to wait until Friday, September 16th at the game.

If you have any questions, please email me at dandksexton@att.net or call me at 440-785-7725.

Thank you,
Debbie Sexton
